    "Further, in 2023, the National Institutes of Health (NIH) introduced a Data Management and Sharing Policy that mandates the sharing of scientific data.",
    "As regulations and institutional reforms are only in early stages, incentives for doing ethical and reproducible work come mostly from the research communities.",
    "Therefore, it is important to give people credit for following the rules of a responsible workflow when reviewing their work in our own communities and spheres of influence.",
    "Part of the maintenance of a project includes documenting the entire process.",
    "Sharing that process frequently, to stakeholders and colleagues alike, rather than only through a written document or oral presentation at the end of the project, can help others learn about both your findings and your workflow."
